                            <comment id="14300953" author="githubbot" created="Mon, 2 Feb 2015 07:11:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user archerrbgh opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/tika/pull/26&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/tika/pull/26&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Added argLine value for maven-surefire-plugin&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Setting a higher maximum amount of memory prevents TestChmExtraction&lt;br/&gt;
    from generating an OutOfMemory error from running out of heap space&lt;br/&gt;
    when running parser tests and trying to install Tika 1.7 on OS X&lt;br/&gt;
    10.10.2. This is to address issue &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-1537&quot; title=&quot;Installation on OSX 10.10.2 generates OutOfMemory Error during parser tests&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;TIKA-1537&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;TIKA-1537&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can merge this pull request into a Git repository by running:&lt;/p&gt;

